>Description:
If I did not have dillo installed and have firefox set as my externel browser, installing dillo while drscheme is running does not then allow me to select dillo in the 'browser' tab in preferences. After restarting drscheme I can choose dillo, however. It would be convenient if I did not have to restart.
>How-To-Repeat:
1. uninstall dillo, if installed
2. start dr scheme
3. note that dillo cannot be selected in preferences -> browser
4. install dillo
5. note that dillo still cannot be selected
6. restart dr scheme
7. select dillo
>Fix:
